answersResultList.title: Mostly Taurus.
answersResultList.resultContent: You understand generally why love makes this a better world, and specifically how it rocks your own world. Even when romance feels inevitable, you're not afraid to give it a healthy shove in the right direction. As much as you like the finer things in life, you don't need them around you 24/7, which is one thing that keeps you from being a total Taurus. While you're happy when people come to you for your brilliant ideas, you're just as happy to step aside and see what they do with them - and of course claim responsibility for the outcome.

answersResultList.title: True Taurus.
answersResultList.resultContent: You're off the charts in all things romantic, you true Taurus, you. Your partner is likely to melt just thinking about your simmering sensuality. Because you want only the best in all things, your life is a perpetual shopping spree. But that weakness for material things won't eclipse your wisdom or compromise your spirit. You remain hardworking and reliable, making full use of your strength and constructive energy. Loyalty is among your most prized possessions, especially when you earn it. Loved ones, friends, associates, and even strangers find you easy to trust, and you will never, ever let them down.

answersResultList.title: Somewhat Taurus.
answersResultList.resultContent: You know how to have fun, which in itself makes you somewhat Taurus. But having fun and coming in under budget? There must be thriftier forces at work in your life. For Taurus, the point of hard work is a lavish wallow in the rewards that it brings. For you, hard work might be about displaying your skills or delegating. Yes, it's practical, but it's hardly the Taurean way of dazzling everyone with results. Also, your opinions may shift too easily. If you were more of a Taurus, you'd plant your feet and argue until the cows come home.

answersResultList.title: Not very Taurus.
answersResultList.resultContent: If you identify with the Bull at all, it's probably out of fear that your neck could be on the chopping block at any minute. Unlike proud, colorful, passionate Taurus, you prefer to keep your head down, not make waves, and not own beautiful things that others would surely want to steal. Being shy is cute, but lose the persecution complex, OK? All this could make you kind of a slacker, which is not very Taurus at all. And if you think you're not worthy of love, check again to make sure whether your ruling planet is actually Venus.

As much as you like the finer things in life, you don't need them around you 24/7, which is one thing that keeps you from being a total Taurus. While you're happy when people come to you for your brilliant ideas, you're just as happy to step aside and see what they do with them - and of course claim responsibility for the outcome.

answersResultList.title: Somewhat Taurus.
answersResultList.resultContent: You know how to have fun, which in itself makes you somewhat Taurus. But having fun and coming in under budget? There must be thriftier forces at work in your life. For Taurus, the point of hard work is a lavish wallow in the rewards that it brings. For you, hard work might be about displaying your skills or delegating. Yes, it's practical, but it's hardly the Taurean way of dazzling everyone with results. Also, your opinions may shift too easily. If you were more of a Taurus, you'd plant your feet and argue until the cows come home.

answersResultList.title: Not very Taurus.
answersResultList.resultContent: If you identify with the Bull at all, it's probably out of fear that your neck could be on the chopping block at any minute. Unlike proud, colorful, passionate Taurus, you prefer to keep your head down, not make waves, and not own beautiful things that others would surely want to steal. Being shy is cute, but lose the persecution complex, OK? All this could make you kind of a slacker, which is not very Taurus at all. And if you think you're not worthy of love, check again to make sure whether your ruling planet is actually Venus.
